<P>Another of the proposed Inscriptions for this Column was a curious composition by Adam Littleton, the compiler of the <hi rend=italics>Lingu&aelig; Latin&aelig; Liber Dictionarius Quadripartitus.</hi>
Lond. <datestruct value="1678--"><year reg="1678">1678</year></datestruct>, <num value="4">4</num>to. on the last leaf of which it is printed with an address; of the whole of which the following is a copy. 
<P>&ldquo;Lectori Benevolo. Quoniam ex Edicto <hi rend=italics>Parliamentario</hi> statutum erat, ut <hi rend=italics>Columna</hi> in memoriam <hi rend=italics>Conflagrationis Londinensis</hi> extrueretur; Ego quoque inter alios, (quod pr&aelig;ficine dico, ut absit invidia verbo) meam Symbolam conjeci, partim <hi rend=italics>Historicam</hi>, i. Narrativam; partim <hi rend=italics>Poeticam</hi>, nimirum <hi rend=italics>Lapidariam;</hi> quo animum erga INCLYTAM URBEM propensum testarer. Eam, ne residua h&aelig;c pagella prorsus vacaret, visum est hic ponere. Ignoscent mihi Nobiles et Ingenui Cives, quod hanc qualemcunque demum <hi rend=italics>Epigraphen</hi> in extremo opere locavi; ubi meminerint vulgati illius dicti, 
<hi rend=italics>Finis Coronat Opus.</hi>

<emph>QUOD FELIX FAUSTUMQUE SIT CIVITATI LONDINENSI.</emph>

<P>Quum Anno <hi rend=italics>Salutis Human&aelig;</hi> MDCLXVI. <hi rend=italics>Reditus</hi> CAROLINI VI. <hi rend=italics>Regni</hi> autem XVIII. Die IV. <hi rend=italics>Nonas Septembres</hi>, fatale et ineluctabile <hi rend=italics>Incendium</hi>, hoc ipso loco in 
<hi rend=italics>pistrina</hi> conceptum, et in viciniam long&egrave; lat&eacute;que, afflantibus sive etiam reflantibus ventis, proseminatum, continuo triduo, <hi rend=italics>Domos, Templa, Basilicas</hi>, c&aelig;ter&aacute;que qu&agrave; <hi rend=italics>Privata</hi>
qu&agrave; <hi rend=italics>Publica</hi> Aedificia, qu&aelig; jam <hi rend=italics>cum bono Deo</hi> renasci videmus, horrendo flammarum liluvio absorbuisset; et <hi rend=italics>Nobilissimam Urbem</hi>, cui nulla Gens aut habuit, aut cert&egrave; (it &agrave; fovere fas est) habitura est parem, maximam partem in cineres redegisset; donec tandem non minore cum miraculo consopitum, qu&agrave;m sub initiis concitatum fuerat, inter medias strages et inhabiles ad resistendum ruinas, ultr&ograve; deflagraret: Placuit ex <hi rend=italics>Senatusconsulto</hi>, in perpetuam rei memoriam decerni <hi rend=italics>Obeliscum</hi> Hunc sive <hi rend=italics>Turrim Speculatoriam</hi>, ex qu&acirc; quoquovers&ugrave;m pateat prospectus Urbicus; qu&ograve; Posteris innotescat Divina c&ugrave;m <hi rend=italics>Severitas</hi> tum <hi rend=italics>Clementia</hi>, cui utrique luculentum Ignis <hi rend=italics>des&aelig;viens</hi> perhibuit testimonium. 
