<P><datestruct value="1783--"><year reg="1783">1783</year></datestruct>. Miss George, now Mrs. Oldmixen, in America; Miss Logan, now Mrs. Gibbs. 
<P><datestruct value="1787--"><year reg="1787">1787</year></datestruct>. Mrs. Farmer, afterwards Mrs. Powell, and now Mrs. Renaud. 
