<P><datestruct value="1788--"><year reg="1788">1788</year></datestruct>. Mr. Kemble, Mrs. Siddons's father, and Mr. Braham. 
<P><datestruct value="1791--"><year reg="1791">1791</year></datestruct>. Cornellys. 
<P><datestruct value="1793--"><year reg="1793">1793</year></datestruct>. Captain Wathen and Miss Leak. 
