<P>From this time the company continued performing without any new name appearing in the bills, till Saturday, the <datestruct VALUE="-07-18"><day reg="18">18th</day> of <month reg="07">July</month></datestruct>, when the following advertisement appears: 
<emph>&ldquo;For the Benefit of Mr. Marr and Miss Hippesley, By a Company of Comedians from the Theatres in London, At the Playhouse in Tankard Street, on Tuesday, the <datestruct VALUE="-07-21"><day reg="21">21st</day> of <month reg="07">July</month></datestruct>, will be performed a Comedy, called THE INCONSTANT, OR THE WAY TO WIN HIM.</emph>

